Description: Create a directory, fill it with data, build models, forecast populations, and visualize the results -- focused on the long-term study of rodent populations at the Portal Project <https://portal.weecology.org/> in Arizona, USA. 'portalcasting' underlies the Portal Predictions Project continuous integration system <https://github.com/weecology/portalpredictions> and website <https://portal.naturecast.org>, as well as providing support for exploring and developing new models in sandbox environments.
URL: https://weecology.github.io/portalcasting/, https://github.com/weecology/portalcasting
